#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-02-09-global-newsletter-48.md:227
#, no-wrap
msgid "**27 MARCH | Global**  \n"
msgstr "**27 MARS | Dans le monde entier**  \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-02-09-global-newsletter-48.md:230
